# Styling Conventions

- Use **Tailwind CSS v4** utility classes exclusively (via `@tailwindcss/vite` plugin)
- Maintain the **monospace font aesthetic** (IBM Plex Mono from Google Fonts)
- Use the accent color from `siteConfig.accentColor` for themed elements
- Follow existing spacing and layout patterns
- Check responsive behavior when updating styles
- Maintain consistent spacing between sections
